text: Had such a great time at Rabbit’s Hole! The place has awesome vibes, great music, and super fun energy. Shoutout to William for being an absolute legend—super friendly and made sure we were having a good time all night. Really appreciated the service. Will definitely be back again!

Was here to celebrate my friend’s birthday.. had this wonderful bartender Ethan attend to us. His recommendations were great, the mixes were on point, and we got our orders without an extremely long wait. Was an overall 5star experience! Thanks Ethan

First time at Rabbit’s Hole with my friends was gagged — in the best way! I usually don’t vibe with clubs in Singapore (Thailand’s scene is hard to beat, you know?), but this place? A full-on serve. The music was on point, the energy was electric, and the crowd was giving!

Special love to Gerald at the outdoor bar — such a sweetheart, super fun to talk to, and his playlist? Baby, we were soulmates. Total slay.

Only one thing — I didn’t know I couldn’t re-enter after going downstairs for toilet since I didn’t get stamped. Would’ve appreciated a heads-up as a first-timer, but no hard feelings.

Overall? ATE. Will definitely bring my Thai peeps here next round!

Had an awesome night at rabbit hole ! Huge shoutout to the server, Ethan —he was super friendly, quick with our drinks, and made great cocktail suggestions. Despite it being a busy night, he handled everything with a smile and made sure we felt taken care of. Service like that makes all the difference. Thanks again, Ethan

such a good vibe place to visit and fabulous service from cute boiiiii Ethan! -
Experience was absolutely perfect,Ethan svc is good and incredibly attentive.
he made amazing drinks cocktail was perfection!
